      h2 Insightful Data on Inventory Valuation
      p Through data analysis and valuation techniques, we show that less than half of a retailer's inventory accounts for 80% of gross margin. Our method delivers accurate market value assessments, ensuring you don’t overpay in taxes on unprofitable inventory.
