      h2 Model Snippet
      p The model used by TBLC is based on a well-established legal and economic framework. The appraisal methodology adheres to Texas Property Tax Code (PTC) and Supreme Court precedents, focusing on determining the profitability of the inventory in question to estimate its market value. This approach ensures that tax assessments are accurate and legally sound, leading to significant reductions in property tax liabilities for clients. The goal is to determine the most probable price a purchaser would pay for the entire inventory unit, reflecting its true market value.
      p
